i18n_gameLayer_6_2: Quick, pick a room and hide, the killer is coming
i18n_wanfaLayer_9_1: Players choose a room to hide from the killer. Once the number of players is met, the killer randomly selects a room and kills everyone inside. The survivors in other rooms evenly share the energy from the killed room {{0}}.
i18n_wanfaLayer_9_3: Players can only choose one room to hide from the killer. After selecting a room, players can switch to a different room before the countdown ends.
i18n_wanfaLayer_9_4: Players can increase the amount of energy invested. The more invested, the more shared (invested energy cannot be decreased).
i18n_wanfaLayer_9_5: 5% of the energy in the killed room is destroyed as a fee.
i18n_rankLayer_10_5: The cutoff point is the last appearance of the killer before midnight on Sunday. The rights of users on this week's ranking will take effect next week and are valid for one week. Players with skins are not included in this week's ranking.
i18n_step4: 4. Killer selects a room to kill
